high_descs: Turn right and walk up to the trash bin
Pick up the tomato from the trash bin
Turn right and walk around the kitchen island to the fridge
Put the tomato into the fridge then remove it
Turn right and walk forward to the microwave on the counter
Put the tomato in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled tomato in the microwave

high_descs: Move straight ahead, and when you're lined up with the window on your right, turn right to stand in front of the trash bin.
Pick up the tomato from behind the apple in the trash bin.
Turn right to move to the dishwasher, then head right again until you get to the fridge.
Open the fridge to place the tomato in the top section, close the door and wait a few seconds, and then remove the tomato.
Turn right and carry the tomato to stand in front of the microwave at the end of the counter on the left.
Open the microwave and place the tomato inside.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Go forward and turn right to face the trash bin to the left of the counter.
Pick up a tomato from inside the trash bin.
Turn around and head to the refrigerator.
Chill the tomato in the freezer compartment for a moment and then take it back out.
Turn right and move to the microwave at the end of the counter.
Place the tomato in to the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Chill a tomato from the trash bin in the freezer and place it in the microwave.
